      <h2>About Pheromones</h2>
      <p>Pheromones are chemical signals that can influence the behavior or physiology of others within the same species. In humans, synthetic pheromones are often used in fragrances with the goal of enhancing attractiveness or influencing social interactions.</p>
      
      <p>While scientific research on human pheromones continues to evolve, many users report positive experiences with these products. Our reviews aim to provide objective information about these products based on collective user experiences and available data.</p>
